# Aero test model: floating octahedron crystal.
# Single named group "crystal" — 6 vertices, 8 triangular faces.
# Drives all three animation channels at once: rotation + scale + position.
# Vertices in block units (0..1), centered at (0.5, 0.5, 0.5).
# Winding: CCW from outside so face normals point outward (top faces up,
# bottom faces down).

o crystal
v 0.5 0.85 0.5
v 0.7 0.5  0.5
v 0.5 0.5  0.7
v 0.3 0.5  0.5
v 0.5 0.5  0.3
v 0.5 0.15 0.5
vt 0 0
vt 1 0
vt 0.5 1
f 1/3 3/1 2/2
f 1/3 4/1 3/2
f 1/3 5/1 4/2
f 1/3 2/1 5/2
f 6/3 2/1 3/2
f 6/3 3/1 4/2
f 6/3 4/1 5/2
f 6/3 5/1 2/2
